      "content": "it's not just about the money though. it's the fact that i've become this joke to everyone. i built this whole life on a lie of success and now the floor has just dropped out. i feel like if i just went back home, everyone would see the failure written all over me. i can't breathe thinking about the shame of it. it feels like there's no way to actually fix it, you know? it's just a permanent stain.",
